message.content:
Here's a healthy meal plan for you this week that doesn't include any of those ingredients:

Monday:
- Breakfast: Greek yogurt with berries, honey, and a drizzle of maple syrup
- Lunch: Quinoa and black bean salad with avocado, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and a lemon dressing
- Dinner: Lentil soup with whole-grain bread and a mixed greens salad

Wednesday:
- Breakfast: Overnight oats with almond milk, chia seeds, and a drizzle of maple syrup
- Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and a lemon dressing
- Dinner: Stuffed bell peppers with quinoa, black beans, and a mixture of herbs and spices

Friday:
- Breakfast: Smoothie bowl with spinach, kale, almond milk, and a drizzle of maple syrup
- Lunch: Caprese sandwich on whole-grain bread with tomato, basil, and mozzarella
- Dinner: Spaghetti squash with turkey and a side salad

Remember to drink plenty of water and eat a balanced diet to keep your body in top shape for the week ahead..
